{"tid":1546381,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"而家開始要有新口號：「廢除八三一框架，立即雙真普選」","createTime":"2019-09-06T09:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T19:14:44.000Z","uid":59815,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1a0cd62e6ea782d3f592a4eb8977ae6a7f5c90","tid":1546381,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:12:24.000Z","msg":"同好多人傾開，佢哋以為五年前 Chinazi 中共提出的「八三一框架」已經被香港議會否決。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大錯特錯！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2015年立法會否決咗嘅只係香港政府提出、依照八三一框架而定的假普選方案。但係人大常委嘅八三一決定仍然係生效。<br />\n<br />\n如果我哋唔講返廢除八三一框架，咁林鄭是旦將2015假普選方案改少少，就話回應咗普選訴求，外國又以為香港贏咗，咁死咗嘅手足係唔會原諒我哋。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好唔記得，2015年西方國家係曾經支持香港袋住先，美國同中國打緊貿易戰，我哋要爭取佢哋支持香港人。但係佢未必同我哋撐真普選到底</span><br />\n<br />\n如果有人問真普選係點做？最簡單，五年前香港人已經有個方案：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><em>公民提名必不可少</em></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廢除八三一，我要雙真普選<br />\n公民提名、議會提名，缺一不可<br />\n不要篩選委員會<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"704ccf8fd3c9be4db5c4eec72076c01f573aef69","tid":1546381,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOryIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=77f87e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"6598e25c82053b5862ef9ee3267edf212cdbc20b","tid":1546381,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:13:40.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"h